question: 다음 포스터에 대한 내용으로 적절하지 않은 것은? (번호)
questionData:

question: 다음 지문에서 전체 내용과 관련없는 문장은? (번호)
questionData: Kartrider: Drift is a game made by NEXON Korea and Nitro Studio. This game was released in 2023, as a successor to the original game, Crazy Racing Kartrider. (1) While Kartrider was vulnerable to defective physics, Kartrider: Drift tried to fix those physics. This little but great fix was made possible by Unreal Engine 4. (2) Corporates who earn more than $100,000 should pay for the Unity Pro plan. By utilizing cutting-edge graphics of Unreal Engine 4, minor details were increased too. (3) For example, 'World Gangnam Street' track copied the street of Gangnam with gimmicks for more fun gameplay. This is not limited to this track, but even forest, village, and moonhill city got a graphical upgrade using shaders and high-polygon 3D models. (4) Furthermore, it has much lower paywalls than the average NEXON game. Maplestory, for instance, requires users to pay at least $100 to decorate their characters. (5) But it's free here, only depending on the user's luck since it's a loot box.
